 <metadata>
  <name>Flandrien Challenge in one day</name>
  <desc>Spreading the Flandrien Challenge over multiple days is to easy for you? You like to go the distance in epic one day rides? Well then, here's a route tailored to your inner ultra-cyclist. Make sure to be awake and alert, because you sometimes go up and down the same segment in order not to make this route a +400 km monster. Always look out for the start and finish lines of each segment. Enjoy!</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Cycling In Flanders</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/25359866"/>
  </author>
  <copyright author="OpenStreetMap contributors">
   <year>2020</year>
   <license>https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright</license>
  </copyright>
  <link href="https://www.strava.com/routes/3017376995738644596"/>
 </metadata>
 <trk>
  <name>Flandrien Challenge in one day</name>
  <desc>Spreading the Flandrien Challenge over multiple days is to easy for you? You like to go the distance in epic one day rides? Well then, here's a route tailored to your inner ultra-cyclist. Make sure to be awake and alert, because you sometimes go up and down the same segment in order not to make this route a +400 km monster. Always look out for the start and finish lines of each segment. Enjoy!</desc>
  <link href="https://www.strava.com/routes/3017376995738644596"/>
  <type>cycling</type>
